@thebrewingsailor9172 it’s the little things that help me related to him. I’m not catholic myself but I grew up in a religious household. Had a bit of “Battlin’ Jack” type tough love where I was expected to follow a path my parents picked out for me, then feeling like I wasn’t measuring up then things just spiraled out from there.

Big reason why the show was so great was cuz of quotes like this: “It ain't how you hit the mat, it's how you get up.” And “Lots of people aren't afraid of dying, when it comes down to it. It's living that scares the crap out of them.”

Little pick me ups when ya need it most from the man without fear. Things like that help kept me going and why I am so appreciative of the show for allowing me to escape for a bit.

